{
  "stem": "17308.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 110.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's when the war started with the East and all this.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And part of the fleet managed to go.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Part of the fleet were-- was destroyed, the French fleet.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Another part didn't listen to the orders.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they went to-- to Africa, you know?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that's where they landed eventually-- landed, eventually, in Marrakesh, and then to Mogador, where they also stayed till the end of the war.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They were also afraid at the time, because the German were battling to get hold of Africa at that point and eventually defeat it.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "When Rommel was defeated, then they felt more secure.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Joseph, did you ever hear from your family in Antwerp?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In wartime?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No more.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I got some message at the beginning, and that was the end of it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, like, one or the letter came through, you know?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was when I was still in Toulouse.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then-- well, I suppose, first, letters were intercepted, you know?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you couldn't get through.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that was the end.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I never heard, afterwards, from them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, at that time-- well, they-- they wrote carefully already, at that time, things [? you ?] [? couldn't ?] [? right ?.] At the beginning, it seemed-- things seemed to be all right.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was at the first stage.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They got back.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I don't know what they managed to do exactly, because it didn't last long, unfortunately.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then they had to get-- they went into hiding.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "As I-- as I mentioned to you, we had a very faithful castle what we trusted 100%.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because we helped them, from nothing, to build up a tremendous business.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I caught, in my information, these people betrayed them.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
